In [140]:
# construct graph, where edge weight is based on set overlap
edge_weight_list = []
for i in range(len(summ_anonymized)):
    for j in range(len(summ_anonymized)):
        if i != j:
            w = len(list(set(summ_anonymized.iloc[i, 1:].values) & set(summ_anonymized.iloc[j, 1:].values))) / max(len(set(summ_anonymized.iloc[i, 1:].values)), len(set(summ_anonymized.iloc[j, 1:].values)))
            edge_weight_list.append(tuple([summ_anonymized.iloc[i, 0], summ_anonymized.iloc[j, 0], w]))
In [246]:
G = nx.Graph()
G.add_weighted_edges_from(edge_weight_list)

pos = nx.spring_layout(G)

plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
nx.draw_networkx(G, pos)
